{
  "stem": "15577.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a period of time when the demographics in the situation was that way, they-- they couldn't send us away on this famous march to death, because the Germans were emptying every camp when the front line was approaching, or was near, near.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were emptying ever every camp and sending the people to the-- on the march to death.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And not too many survived the march of death.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now we couldn't be sent, because the front line was such a way that there was no way out of it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We-- we could only stay or-- or be killed on the place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So as we were told, there came an order from Berlin to shot-- to finish with us on the place.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] this is another famous story.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] The people thought what to do, again, the people who were influentials and led together with Schindler.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they came to the conclusion that only one solution is to send away the commanding officer out of the camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And to send him away, to bring him to go to somewhere that is a very big probability that he won't come back because of the-- of the-- front line.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this-- the decision fell, and there was made a false march order for the commanding officer, that he should come to a place where we understood-- or they understood-- that if he came there, he cannot go-- he cannot come back.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the forge was made-- it was written on the machine-- the special stamp was made in order to make it very real.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the stamp was made by-- by a man who was with us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And who afterwards, or now, was a judge in the superior court of Israel.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
